data.description: Welcome to your own piece of paradise in the heart of Hollywood Hills, a highly sought after Hollywood area, this updated 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers white ceramic tile floors throughout, new roof(2022) and AC(2020); Impact windows that allow plenty of natural light, large corner lot with beautiful landscape, and private backyard. Near to great schools such as, Chaminade Madonna College Preparatory School, Nativity Elementary School, The Jewish Academy. Located near Memorial hospital, the Hardrock casino, downtown, beaches, emergency services, and Fort Lauderdale international airport, easy access to major highways connecting you to neighboring cities of Miami and Ft Lauderdale. don't miss the opportunity to own your dream home. No home owners association. Furniture included.
